The '''Ministry of Agriculture Jihad''' ({{lang-fa|وزارت جهاد کشاورزی}} ''Vezārat-e Jahād-e Keshāvarzī'') is an [[Iran]]ian government body established in 2001 responsible for the oversight of [[Agriculture in Iran]]. The ministry has been called [[Jihad of Construction]] but it was merged with agriculture ministry in 2001 to form the Ministry of Agricultural Jihad.
